Message.Title: Good Morning From My Free Speech Garden In Philadelphia
Message.Msg: Everything is wonderful in my free speech garden. I put every plant in its place, in its row. Some I water and others I let get very hot and dry. Some plants are sweet but a few are very bitter. It is not for the plants to know they are salad. They live their days sweating soil. I certainly live my days as I choose. No mono crops. No garden trolls. No GMOs. I hope that helps.
